    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8390029>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Nototanoides trifurcatus, holotype (USNM 222507), female.A, antennule (partial illustrated). Nototanoides oliveri sp. nov. paratype ovigerous female. B, antennule; C, enlargement of antennular articles 2 to 3, showing presence of aesthetascs, ventral view; D, antenna; E, enlargement of bipinnate spiniform seta; F, labrum; G, left mandible; H; right mandible; Scale bars = 0.1 mm for A–D, F–H." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8390029/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

